-- MOVES-Northland Capital names Gerald Beaney as corporate finance head
-- 
-- Tue Sep 16, 2014 07:54AM EDT
-- None



Sept 16 (Reuters) - London-based investment bank Northland Capital Partners Ltd said it appointed Gerald Beaney as head of corporate finance with immediate effect.

Beaney has previously worked as partner and head of capital markets at Grant Thornton UK LLP.